<%= render partial: 'notices/shared/paragraph_with_headers', :locals => { contents: ["Before a hearing decision is made, you can stop your appeal through any of the methods described above for requesting the appeal.  If you stop your appeal based on a new decision arrived upon during your meeting with #{Settings.site.short_name} representatives, your new eligibility will reflect the agreed upon changes.    However, if you stop your appeal before you meet with #{Settings.site.short_name} representatives or before #{Settings.site.short_name} has changed its decision, the original decision will be implemented as written in the notice you first received prior to appeal."], heading: 'Ending Your Appeal Early', sub_heading: ''} %>

